data.description: Spacious home with an open floor plan. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Solid home built with cement exterior walls. A newer 36x24 shop w/loft storage, work bench and plumbed for a bathroom. Over 1 acre of land w/plenty of space for your RV, boat, toys and more! Fully fenced and cross fenced. Tile floors throughout the house, no carpet. Living room has a wood burning stove. Roomy kitchen with a ton of cabinet space & updated SS appliances! All appliances included. Hot tub room w/bathroom. Many upgrades! AC unit was replaced 4-5 years ago and blows ice cold. Newer water softener with a UV system to kill bacteria. Solar is leased at $205/month. Solar water heater that is paid off. Updated exterior paint and shutters. Smart fire alarms. Full length back patio & enclosed patio make a great space for entertaining. BBQ grill included. An abundance of storage. 2 sheds and a well house at the rear of the property. A large outbuilding w/carport for even more storage! Ample opportunity here!
